						<p>On a slab at the entrance of the Lakshmīnarasiṁha temple.</p>						

						<p>. • • • • (In characters of 13th century).</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Mentions Śāntaśiva-dēśika of Nava-Gōḷakī-maṭha and seems to refer to a gift of land made for his memorial.</p>						

